OL,3,CThe whisky distillery helping put town
OL,4,Con the tourist map
OL,6,FIt is now also home to the county's
OL,7,Ffirst single malt whisky distillery.
OL,9,FChris Ferguson, experience director
OL,10,Ffor Ad Gefrin, said: "The ancient site
OL,11,Fof Ad Gefrin hadn't had its story
OL,12,Ftold. No-one had thought to make
OL,13,Fsingle malt whisky in Northumberland
OL,14,Fbefore.
OL,16,F"We are the North East's first single
OL,17,Fmalt distillery and an Anglo Saxon
OL,18,Fmuseum. So we celebrate the best of
OL,19,Fthe region.
