OL,3,CThe whisky distillery helping put town
OL,4,Con the tourist map
OL,6,F"It's an unknown. It's a museum with a
OL,7,Fdistillery on the side - that's not
OL,8,Fbeen done before and it's in a part of
OL,9,FNorthumberland that hasn't had this
OL,10,Fkind of offer before. So it was a risk
OL,11,Fon lots of levels."
OL,13,FIt opened a year ago, offering people
OL,14,Fthe chance to find out more about the
OL,15,Fdistilling process, as well as the
OL,16,FAnglo Saxon history of the area.
