OL,3,CThe whisky distillery helping put town
OL,4,Con the tourist map
OL,6,FThe distillery's cask warehouse has
OL,7,Fspace for around 12,000 barrels - but
OL,8,Fit will still be two to three years
OL,9,Fbefore the first are ready for
OL,10,Fconsumption.
OL,12,FHead distiller Ben Murphy said: "The
OL,13,Fgame of whisky is a long one. There's
OL,14,Fno quick way of doing what we're doing.
OL,16,F"There is a reason it's done this way
OL,17,F- the length of time gives a maturity
OL,18,Fand a flavour profile to our spirit
OL,19,Fthat you can't fully achieve by
OL,20,Frapidly ageing. For us, it works."
