OL,3,CThe whisky distillery helping put town
OL,4,Con the tourist map
OL,6,FWhile still in its infancy, it is
OL,7,Falready attracting visitors, last year
OL,8,Fbringing about 64,000 people to the
OL,9,Ftown.
OL,11,F"It's just been a brilliant year. It's
OL,12,Fbeen fantastic to welcome people and
OL,13,Fto bring this many people to Wooler
OL,14,Fhas had an impact on the town," added
OL,15,FMr Ferguson.
OL,17,F"We want to end up in a place where
OL,18,FWooler really is on people's first
OL,19,Fchoice list of places to visit when
OL,20,Fthey come to Northumberland."
