OL,4,Con the tourist map
OL,6,FAmong those sharing the success are
OL,7,Fother businesses in the town.
OL,9,FJackie Maxwell, who runs Doddington
OL,10,FDairy Milk Bar, said: "We've seen a
OL,11,Fbig influx of visitors to Wooler. This
OL,12,Flast Easter weekend Wooler was buzzing
OL,13,Fwith people.
OL,15,F"We welcome this business that was
OL,16,Fcoming to Wooler and they tried to
OL,17,Fencourage locals to be part of that
OL,18,Fjourney so it's something we've been
OL,19,Fon since the very beginning. As a
OL,20,Flocal business we feel part of that
OL,21,Fjourney too."
